    %p Sponsors that don’t make the date will still appear on the website and be announced via Twitter & Facebook.

    %h3 Your Sponsorship Will Help Benefit the Community
    
    %p This year any donations go to help benefit <a href="http://www.speakupmag.org/">Speak Up Magazine</a>, a local 501(c) (3) public charty. Speak Up is a street magazine for Charlotte sold primarily by homeless and low-income people. By selling Speak Up, homeless individuals can earn a livable income through hard work, helping them to become financially responsible, gain a sense of pride and live with dignity and hope. There are over 100 street newspapers and magazines in 40 countries. In the last 15 years, these publications have impacted the lives of over 250,000 homeless men and women.